The paper deals with computer vision techniques for estimating driver gaze regions without using eye movement. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves human-computer interaction (HCI) and robotics (RO) as it aims to develop an advanced driver assistance system. The paper uses machine learning techniques for classification, which falls under the category of machine learning (LG) and artificial intelligence (AI).
